reviewText: I love Tom and Jerry The Movie it's really cool that there are two movies and as an added bonus some Tom and Jerry cartoon episodes on this DVD so I'm very happy with this

bought this for the tom and jerry the movie. a great film collection. the ring was not a bad movie either. great value for the price. the tom and jerry movie was still just as good as when I saw it years back. recommended for future generations of children to see.
